From: Mario Limonciello <mario.limonciello@dell.com>
Date: Tue, 13 Dec 2016 15:28:02 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Disable PrivateNetwork on systemd service

commit e34654e1 caused a regression that hotplugging devices no
longer worked.

Disabling systemd PrivateNetwork confinement resolves this.
---
 data/fwupd.service.in | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/data/fwupd.service.in b/data/fwupd.service.in
index 5e706c8..f3306df 100644
--- a/data/fwupd.service.in
+++ b/data/fwupd.service.in
@@ -9,5 +9,4 @@ ConditionPathExists=/var/lib/fwupd/pending.db
 Type=dbus
 BusName=org.freedesktop.fwupd
 ExecStart=@servicedir@/fwupd/fwupd
-PrivateNetwork=yes
 PrivateTmp=yes
